      "description": "$34,900 - Good condition overall. Clean and well-kept for its age, with only typical light cosmetic wear. Runs and drives properly and presents as a solid, above-average example, though not a mint showpiece. A good fit for someone looking for a nice usable car without paying top-of-market money.",
