    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Offered at $44,900, this older vehicle is in truly mint condition and stands out for how exceptionally well-preserved it is. The exterior presents beautifully with strong paint, clean trim, and no notable cosmetic issues, while the interior is equally impressive with minimal wear and a well-kept, like-new appearance. It has clearly been cared for properly, and a buyer can expect a vehicle that feels far above what is typical for its age, both in presentation and overall condition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Solid fair-condition driver being sold honestly as a usable, presentable car rather than a standout example. It shows visible cosmetic wear inside and out consistent with age, and buyers should expect the usual blemishes, signs of use, and some deferred upkeep that often comes with a vehicle in this condition. That said, it remains a practical option for someone looking for dependable transportation at a more accessible price point, and it should suit a buyer who values function over perfection.",
      "price": 18900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation at an affordable price point. A sensible choice for buyers seeking value, it presents an opportunity to own a dependable car without a major investment. Priced to reflect its overall condition, it\u2019s a practical option for commuting, light use, or a project-minded buyer looking for solid potential.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right buyer? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants simple, usable transport or a great little project to tinker with. It has the kind of honest character you expect from a well-used vehicle, and for the money it offers a lot of value. If you want something inexpensive and approachable without spending a fortune, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with a strong-running engine, responsive automatic transmission, and dependable cold-start behavior. This car shows its age cosmetically, but the powertrain feels eager, tracks straight, and makes a practical platform for commuting, a backup vehicle, or a project build. Suspension and braking deliver predictable road manners, and it offers good utility for someone who values function over finish. If you want an affordable car with real everyday usability and room to improve over time, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    }
